snippet.title: A ticket to Mars, with a catch
snippet.description: A pair of scientists say they know a way to speed the 20-plus year timetable for sending an astronaut to Mars. Just give the astronaut a one-way ticket. Our friends at the Associated Press have the details of the proposal from professors at Washington State

snippet.title: Tickets on sale Saturday for Bruno Mars, Janelle Monae at The Rave
snippet.description: Tickets will go on sale at 10 a.m. Saturday for a concert by two of today's most compelling live performers, Bruno Mars and Janelle Monae. The singers will share a bill as part of the Hooligans in Wondaland tour at 7 p.m. May 24 in the Eagles Ballroom,
